1. Extract domain model:
- Core entity classes:
  - `Task`: the main domain entity representing a work item.
  - `TaskStatus`: task lifecycle states (`TODO`, `IN_PROGRESS`, `REVIEW`, `DONE`).
  - `TaskPriority`: urgency categories (`LOW`, `MEDIUM`, `HIGH`, `URGENT`).
